# PHOENIX PROTOCOL - UNIFIED GATEWAY CONFIG V8.1 (JURISTI REFRESH FIX)
# 1. FIX: Added header_up directives to ensure backend recognizes HTTPS and correct Host.
# 2. STATUS: End-to-End Infrastructure Ready.

{
